#: index.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kronometer; 2.1"
msgstr "&kronometer; 2.1"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kronometer; is a stopwatch application. It can be used for basic tasks like "
"timer start/pause/resume, as well as lap times recording."
msgstr ""
"&kronometer; on stopperirakendus, Seda saab kasutada nii selliste lihtsate "
"asjade jaoks nagu taimeri käivitamine, pausile panemine ja taaskäivitamine "
"kui ka ringiaegade salvestamiseks."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kronometer; is able to save a complete session (timer and lap times) and to "
"restore it later."
msgstr ""
"&kronometer; võib salvestada terve seansi (taimeri ja ringiajad) ning "
"taastada need hiljem."

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"
msgstr "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "Kronometer"
msgstr "Kronometer"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "stopwatch"
msgstr "stopper"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Sissejuhatus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kronometer; is a simple stopwatch application. It is meant to be simple and "
"pleasant to use, thanks to a use cases driven development."
msgstr ""
"&kronometer; on lihtne stopperirakendus. See on kujundatud lihtsa ja "
"meeldivana, kuna arenduse taga seisavad praktilised vajadused."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kronometer; main features are the following:"
msgstr "&kronometer;i põhiomadused on järgmised:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kronometer; provides a timer that can be started, paused, resumed and reset."
msgstr ""
"&kronometer; pakub taimerit, mida saab käivitada, pausile panna, "
"taaskäivitada ja lähtestada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kronometer; allows you to record lap times and export them to a file."
msgstr ""
"&kronometer; võimaldab salvestada ringiaegu ja eksportida need failina."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kronometer; allows you to save a session and restore it later."
msgstr "&kronometer; võimaldab seansi salvestada ja selle hiljem taastada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kronometer; allows you to copy the timer numbers from its display."
msgstr "&kronometer; võimaldab kopeerida oma liidesest aegu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "Usage"
msgstr "Kasutamine"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid "General Usage"
msgstr "Üldine kasutamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kronometer; main use case is of course the interaction with the timer. You "
"can start/pause/resume the timer by clicking on the proper actions in the "
"toolbar or in the &kronometer; menu."
msgstr ""
"&kronometer;i põhiline kasutamisala on loomulikult stopperina. Taimeri saab "
"käivitada, pausile panna ja taaskäivitada, kui klõpsata vastava toimingu "
"ikoonile tööriistaribal või valida see &kronometer;i menüüst."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Even simpler, you can use the keyboard instead of the mouse: you start the "
"timer with the keyboard's <keycap>Space</keycap> and you pause the timer "
"with <keycap>Space</keycap> too. You might recognize this behavior from many "
"media player applications."
msgstr ""
"Mis veel lihtsam: hiire asemel võib kasutada isegi kiirklahve. Taimeri saab "
"käivitada klaviatuurilt <keycap>tühikuklahv</keycap>iga, pausile panna "
"samuti <keycap>tühikuklahv</keycap>iga. Selline võimalus peaks olema tuttav "
"paljudest meediamängija-rakendustest."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By pressing the &Enter; key when the timer is running, you freeze that "
"particular time and you create a new <emphasis>lap</emphasis> time. These "
"times are always visible in the table on the left of the application, where "
"you can sort them by clicking the <emphasis>Lap time</emphasis> column's "
"header. You can also add a custom text annotation to each lap, by double-"
"clicking the cells within the <emphasis>Note</emphasis> column."
msgstr ""
"Kui vajutada taimeri töötamise ajal klahvi &Enter;, külmutatakse parajasti "
"olnud aeg ning luuakse uus <emphasis>ringiaeg</emphasis>. Need ajad on kogu "
"aeg näha rakenduse vasakul servas tabelis, kus neid saab sortida, kui "
"klõpsata veerupäisele <emphasis>Ringiaeg</emphasis>. Samuti saab igale "
"ringile lisada meelepärase tekstilise märkuse, milleks tuleb teha "
"topeltklõps vastava ringi rea taga veerus <emphasis>Märkus</emphasis>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The menubar (hidden by default) provides access to all commands and "
"configuration options. The menubar can be toggled with <guimenuitem>Show "
"Menubar</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>M</keycap></"
"keycombo>) from the <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> menu or the menu button in "
"the toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Menüüriba (vaikimisi peidetud) võimadlab kasutada kõiki käske ja "
"seadistamisvalikuid. Menüüriba näitamist saab lülitada kas käsuga "
"<guimenuitem>Menüüriba näitamine</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>M</keycap></keycombo>), mille leiab menüüst "
"<guimenu>Seadistused</guimenu>, või tööriistaribal leiduva menüünupuga."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save and Restore Sessions"
msgstr "Seansi salvestamine ja taastamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you pause a running stopwatch you create a session: a stopwatch time "
"and zero or more lap times. You can save a session and you can restore it "
"later."
msgstr ""
"Töötavat stopperit peatades lood seansi, mis koosneb stopperi ajast ning "
"nullist või enamast ringiajast. Seansi saab salvestada ja hiljem uuesti "
"taastada."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save a Session"
msgstr "Seansi salvestamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pause a running stopwatch, then click on the <guibutton>Save As</guibutton> "
"button in the <guimenu>File</guimenu> menu. You can choose a name for the "
"session that you are going to save."
msgstr ""
"Peata töötav stopper ja seejärel klõpsa nupule <guibutton>Salvesta kui</"
"guibutton>, mille leiab menüüst <guimenu>Fail</guimenu>. Seejärel saad "
"salvestatavale seansile valida ka nime."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid "Restore a Session"
msgstr "Seansi taastamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click the <guibutton>Open</guibutton> button on the toolbar or in the "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> menu. Then choose an existing session to be loaded "
"from the session's dialog."
msgstr ""
"Klõpsa nupule <guibutton>Ava</guibutton> tööriistaribal või menüüs "
"<guimenu>Fail</guimenu>. Seejärel vali seansidialoogist seanss, mida soovid "
"laadida."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid "Update a Session"
msgstr "Seansi uuendamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the session is restored, you can resume the stopwatch and you can "
"record new lap times. If you want to save the updated session, you can "
"simply click the <guibutton>Save</guibutton> button in the <guimenu>File</"
"guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"Kui seanss on taastatud, võid stopperi uuesti käivitada ning salvestada uusi "
"ringiaegu. Kui soovid nüüd uuendatud seansi salvestada, klõpsa lihtsalt "
"nupule <guibutton>Salvesta</guibutton>, mille leiad menüüst <guimenu>Fail</"
"guimenu>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edit a Session"
msgstr "Seansi muutmine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click the <guibutton>Open</guibutton> button on the toolbar or in the "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> menu. If you select an existing session in the "
"session's dialog, you will be able to:"
msgstr ""
"Klõpsa nupule <guibutton>Ava</guibutton> tööriistaribal või menüüs "
"<guimenu>Fail</guimenu>. Kui valid seansidialoogis olemasoleva seansi, on "
"võimalik ette võtta järgmisi toiminguid:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rename the session, by double-clicking on its name."
msgstr "Seansi nime muutmine, tehes nimel topeltklõpsu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete the session, by pressing <keycap>Del</keycap>."
msgstr "Seansi kustutamine vajutades klahvi <keycap>Del</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:146
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Add a note the the session or edit it."
msgid "Add a note to the session or edit it."
msgstr "Märkuse lisamine seansile või selle muutmine"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid "Additional Features"
msgstr "Lisavõimalused"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid "Export Lap Times"
msgstr "Ringiaegade eksport"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you record one or more lap times, the export features in the "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> menu is made available, under the entry "
"<guimenuitem>Export laps as</guimenuitem>. Click on it and then choose a "
"name for the exported file. You can export in the Comma Separated Values "
"(CSV) format or in the JSON one."
msgstr ""
"Kui oled salvestanud vähemalt ühe ringiaja, ilmuvad menüüsse <guimenu>Fail</"
"guimenu> ekspordivõimalused kirjena <guimenuitem>Ringide eksport</"
"guimenuitem>. Klõpsa sellele ja vali eksporditava faili nimi. Eksportida "
"saab nii komadega eraldatud väärtuste (CSV) vormingus kui ka JSON-failina."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid "Clipboard Support"
msgstr "Lõikepuhvri toetus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kronometer; is able to copy the current stopwatch time to the system "
"clipboard. Use the <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> key "
"combination or the <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem> entry in the "
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"&kronometer; võib kopeerida aktiivse stopperiaja süsteemsesse "
"lõikepuhvrisse. Selleks kasuta kiirklahvi <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>C</"
"keycap></keycombo> või käsku <guimenuitem>Kopeeri</guimenuitem> menüüs "
"<guimenu>Redigeerimine</guimenu>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuration"
msgstr "Seadistamine"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid "Settings Dialog"
msgstr "Seadistustedialoog"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kronometer; is customizable in many aspects. You can open the settings "
"dialog clicking on the <guimenuitem>Configure &kronometer;</guimenuitem> "
"entry in the <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> menu. The settings dialog is "
"organized in the following categories."
msgstr ""
"&kronometer;it saab mitmeti seadistada. Seadistustedialoogi saab avada, kui "
"klõpsata kirjele <guimenuitem>&kronometer;i seadistamine</guimenuitem> "
"menüüs <guimenu>Seadistused</guimenu>. Seadistustedialoog on jagatud "
"järgmistesse kategooriatesse."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid "General Settings"
msgstr "Üldised seadistused"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the general settings page you can find the settings for the stopwatch and "
"for the laps. Under the stopwatch tab you can set your preferred time format "
"for the stopwatch display. You can choose whether to show hours, minutes or "
"second fractions (while seconds are always shown). &kronometer; supports "
"time granularity up to millisecond, although this requires high CPU usage "
"due to the high refresh rate of the User Interface."
msgstr ""
"Üldiste seadistuste kaardil leiab stopperit ja ringe puudutavad seadistused. "
"Stopperikaardil saab määrata meelepärase ajaesituse vormingu. Seal saab "
"valida, kas näidatakse tunde, minuteid ja sekundi murdosasid (sekundeid "
"ennast näidatakse alati). &kronometer; toetab ajaühikuid kuni "
"millisekunditeni, ehkki see seab kasutajaliidese väga suure "
"värskendamissageduse tõttu protsessorile tubli koormuse."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Within the laps tab you can enable or disable the laps recording feature. If "
"the laps are enabled, you can choose their time format, whether to show "
"their notes and whether to show their absolute times, which are the "
"stopwatch times when they were recorded."
msgstr ""
"Ringide kaardil saab nende salvestamise sisse või välja lülitada. Kui ringid "
"on lubatud, saab valida ka nende ajavormingu, samuti selle, kas näidatakse "
"nende märkusi ja kas näidatakse absoluutset aega ehk stopperiaega "
"salvestamise ajal."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid "Font Settings"
msgstr "Fondiseadistused"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the font settings page you can customize the font of the stopwatch "
"display. You can choose different font families, styles and sizes for each "
"timer component (hours, minutes, &etc;). By default every timer component "
"will use the same font, according the current default font in the system."
msgstr ""
"Fondiseadistuste kaardil saab määrata stopperil kasutatava fondi. Taimeri "
"igale osale (tunnid, minutid &etc;) saab valida eraldi fondipere, stiili ja "
"suuruse. Vaikimisi kasutavad kõik osad siiski ühesugust fonti, milleks on "
"süsteemi vaikefont."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid "Color Settings"
msgstr "Värviseadistused"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the color settings page you can customize the default color of the "
"stopwatch display. You can change the background color and the text color. "
"The default colors will respect the currently selected system's theme."
msgstr ""
"Värviseadistuste kaardil saab määrata meelepärase stopperi värvi. Muuta saab "
"tausta ja teksti värvi. Vaikimisi kasutatakse süsteemis parajasti kehtiva "
"teema värvilahendust."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kde; Built-in Settings"
msgstr "&kde; sisseehitatud seadistused"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kronometer; makes use of the standard &kde; configuration tools. You find "
"them in the <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> menu, under the "
"<guimenuitem>Configure shortcuts</guimenuitem> and <guimenuitem>Configure "
"Toolbars</guimenuitem> entries. They allow you to change the shortcuts of "
"the &kronometer;'s actions, and to change the position of the toolbar and "
"its content."
msgstr ""
"&kronometer; kasutab mitmeid &kde; standardseid seadistusvahendeid. Need "
"leiab menüüst <guimenu>Seadistused</guimenu> kirjete alt "
"<guimenuitem>Kiirklahvide seadistamine</guimenuitem> ja "
"<guimenuitem>Tööriistaribade seadistamine</guimenuitem>. Nende abil saab "
"muuta &kronometer;i toimingute kiirklahve ning tööriistaribade asukohta ja "
"sisu."

